================
Enhancement of ALSA firewire stack
================

Description
========
June 2014, ALSA, Linux sound subsystem gained an enhancement of support for Firewire sound devices and Linux 3.16 merged it. This is a report of my work for the enhancement and also my memo.


Status
========
Under writing the whole section.


How to read
========
Please refer to firewire.pdf. I'll keep firewire.pdf is always the latest output.

how to build
========
Need some softwares process text and images:
 - GNU Make
 - LaTeX
 - Inkscape, to generate from svg
 - Graphviz, to generate from dot

Then execute make.

